  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. This package contains a ValidationResult whose detailed narrative describes the experimental campaign and simulation comparison, but for which no structured prov:wasGeneratedBy Activity link is present — the prose is intended to read as sufficient provenance, masking the missing structured link.",
